title: Effect of probiotics on canine gastrointestinal health
summary: This study examines the impact of probiotic supplementation on dogs with chronic gastrointestinal issues.
clinical_bottom_line: Probiotics showed significant improvement in reducing GI symptoms in 75% of cases.
pubmed_id: Smith J, Jones A, Brown K

title: Comparative analysis of pain management in feline orthopedic surgery
summary: Research comparing different analgesic protocols for cats undergoing orthopedic procedures.
clinical_bottom_line: Multi-modal analgesia provides superior pain control compared to single-agent protocols.
